---
title: Autonomous Agent - High Level Architecture
---

graph TB

    CLI["Copilot CLI SDK<br/>────────────────────<br/>LLM access (GPT-4, etc.)<br/>Tool execution runtime<br/>Session management"]

    AGENT["Agent Loop<br/>────────────────────<br/>1. Check priority mailbox<br/>2. Process pending work items<br/>3. Check normal mailbox<br/>4. Sleep until next interval"]

    MAILBOX["External Mailbox<br/>────────────────────<br/>mailbox/to_[host]_[role]/<br/>  priority/ normal/ background/<br/>Multi-agent coordination"]

    WORKSPACE["Workspace Manager<br/>────────────────────<br/>Work item queue (pending/done)<br/>Session context persistence<br/>File and state management"]

    EXECUTOR["Work Item Executor<br/>────────────────────<br/>Delegates to LLM via SDK<br/>Timeout and retry handling<br/>Completion tracking"]

    CLI --- AGENT
    AGENT --> MAILBOX
    AGENT --> WORKSPACE
    WORKSPACE --> EXECUTOR
    EXECUTOR --> CLI
